a fantasy icon representing a spell scroll as a rolled parchment scroll, partially unrolled, revealing arcane symbols and magical writing inside

focus on a single object, compact and cohesive design, no scattered items

the scroll is simple and practical, not overly ornate, with visible magical markings

no straps, no ribbons, no ties, no bindings

style: stylized realism, world of warcraft inspired UI icon, bold shapes, clean edges, soft painterly shading, slightly exaggerated forms, high contrast

materials: aged parchment, ink markings, subtle magical energy

background: pure black void, no texture, no gradient, no environment, completely empty background

composition: centered, scroll fills most of the frame, square 1:1 aspect ratio, no border, no frame

magical intensity reflects spell level: lower levels have faint glow and minimal runes, higher levels have brighter glow, more defined arcane symbols, and a more open scroll

